  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><i>In realms of quack, where things were great,<br>Abruptly things have changed ones fate...</i></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/dc82b41272ea83dc706de3ccfc6c10de.webp?t=1727281633\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >No Ducks Given is an INDIE mix of a MATH PUZZLES & TOWER DEFENSE. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Use you <strong>brain</strong> and <strong>fast calculation skills</strong> to earn as much GOLD as you can!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/7acaeb563b312cfee95c8e569d3b8226.poster.avif?t=1727281633\" width=600 height=300 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/7acaeb563b312cfee95c8e569d3b8226.webm?t=1727281633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/7acaeb563b312cfee95c8e569d3b8226.mp4?t=1727281633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore <strong>8 DIFFERENT LEVELS</strong>, face <strong>8 AWESOME BOSSES</strong> and complete the <strong>FULL STORY</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/a66a5573fef5bee4a572d90d4b488982.webp?t=1727281633\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In NDG you will find 3 completely different and UPGRADABLE types of Ducks:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/d82963850dfe6cd932e7cf2d095ba89c.poster.avif?t=1727281633\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/d82963850dfe6cd932e7cf2d095ba89c.webm?t=1727281633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/d82963850dfe6cd932e7cf2d095ba89c.mp4?t=1727281633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>PUNCHER</strong></u> // Basic battle Duck, cheap and effective. When upgraded - wears sandals, karate headband, cool sunglasses and... goes bananas!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>FREEZER</u></strong> // Slowing Duck, loves winter sports and warm scarves. Has range of 3 rows and when upgraded - shoots only unfrozen ones, while dealing small, additional damage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>GOLDY</u></strong> // Expensive but laying golden eggs aristocrate. If upgraded, wears an awesome crown, fancy pantaloons and speeds up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each of them have their own strenght and weaknesess. It's up to you to figure out which of them will become useful in what situation.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The tactics are limitless!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In NDG you will also encounter 3 completely different TYPES of Enemies:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/a2261599141de8e1097dbda9f14e4058.poster.avif?t=1727281633\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/a2261599141de8e1097dbda9f14e4058.webm?t=1727281633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/a2261599141de8e1097dbda9f14e4058.mp4?t=1727281633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>WALKER</u></strong> // Most common Zombie, present in every situation, core meat grinder in every army. Altough it has average walking speed, damage and HP, it can be dangerous when few of them are comming in the same row.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>RUNER</u></strong> // His low damage is made up for it with  high speed and mobility. It likes comming in packs so be prepared. He's biggest weakness is being slowed down by a Freezer.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>FATTY</u></strong> / Huge, slooow but very resistant to all your perk. It has plenty of HP but the good thing is he uses two rows so it can be hit by multiple Ducks. It likes to come at the end of a wave so be carefull.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/d9f5a8595f7db527c9810bf695904be3.webp?t=1727281633\" width=617 height=57 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fight EPIC battles, use different tactics and <strong>MAKE THEM HELL!</strong> Stay strong agains many <strong>WAVES</strong> of maaany hungry enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/e983face7f7aa1906852df6302a0f5db.poster.avif?t=1727281633\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/e983face7f7aa1906852df6302a0f5db.webm?t=1727281633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/e983face7f7aa1906852df6302a0f5db.mp4?t=1727281633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There are lots of different aproaches and play styles. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >They are also in-game <strong>CHALLENGES</strong> and <strong>28 ACHIEVEMENTS</strong> if you are up to a little dare.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >And at the end of every level, challenge yourself agains <strong>MIGHTY BOSSES</strong>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/0f1bdd527b2874bb426be26ca23cf0b6.poster.avif?t=1727281633\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/0f1bdd527b2874bb426be26ca23cf0b6.webm?t=1727281633\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3132460/extras/0f1bdd527b2874bb426be26ca23cf0b6.mp4?t=1727281633\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >///</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >This is my first game and I'm HONORED that you tried it and i hope you like it!<br>If you found a bug, or have any suggestions, please contact me at .<br><br>Thanks again and see you in NDG2! :)</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><strong>GOOD QUACK TRAVELER!</strong></i></p>",
